<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>開普勒行星運動定律 | Kepler's Laws of Planetary Motion</title>
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS for styling -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- MathJax for rendering physics formulas -->
    <script id="MathJax-script" async src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        /* Custom styles for sliders to look better in dark mode */
        input[type=range] {
            accent-color: #3b82f6;
        }
        .glow {
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px 5px rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.4);
        }
        /* Ensure canvas remains sharp */
        canvas {
            image-rendering: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 h-screen w-screen overflow-hidden flex flex-col font-sans selection:bg-blue-500 selection:text-white">

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="flex-none flex justify-between items-center p-3 md:p-4 bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800 shadow-md">
        <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400 tracking-wide" data-i18n="title">
            開普勒行星運動定律
        </h1>
        <div class="flex gap-2 md:gap-3">
            <button id="btn-info" class="px-3 md:px-4 py-2 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-amber-950 rounded-md transition duration-200 font-bold flex items-center shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/20">
                <span data-i18n="infoBtn">說明</span>
            </button>
            <button id="btn-lang" class="px-3 md:px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-md transition duration-200 font-medium">
                繁/Eng
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col lg:flex-row p-2 md:p-4 gap-4 overflow-hidden min-h-0">
        
        <!-- Controls Sidebar (Moved to Left) -->
        <div class="w-full lg:w-80 flex flex-col gap-4 bg-slate-900 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 shadow-md flex-shrink-0 overflow-y-auto h-auto lg:h-full max-h-[40vh] lg:max-h-full">
            
            <!-- Presets Dropdown -->
            <div>
                <label class="flex justify-between text-xs md:text-sm font-medium mb-1">
                    <span data-i18n="preset" class="text-slate-300">預設天體：</span>
                </label>
                <select id="preset-select" class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-600 rounded p-2 text-sm text-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500 cursor-pointer">
                    <option value="custom" data-i18n="presetCustom">自訂 (Custom)</option>
                    <option value="mercury" data-i18n="presetMercury">水星 (Mercury)</option>
                    <option value="venus" data-i18n="presetVenus">金星 (Venus)</option>
                    <option value="earth" data-i18n="presetEarth" selected>地球 (Earth)</option>
                    <option value="mars" data-i18n="presetMars">火星 (Mars)</option>
                    <option value="jupiter" data-i18n="presetJupiter">木星 (Jupiter)</option>
                    <option value="halley" data-i18n="presetHalley">哈雷彗星 (Halley's Comet)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <!-- Law 1 & 3: Shape & Orbit Size -->
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div>
                    <label class="flex justify-between text-xs md:text-sm font-medium mb-1">
                        <span data-i18n="semiMajor">軌道半長軸 (a)：</span>
                        <span id="val-a" class="text-blue-300 font-mono">1.00 AU</span>
                    </label>
                    <input type="range" id="slider-a" min="0.1" max="20" step="0.1" value="1.0" class="w-full cursor-pointer">
                    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1" data-i18n="law3Desc">影響行星公轉週期 (第三定律)</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="flex justify-between text-xs md:text-sm font-medium mb-1">
                        <span data-i18n="eccentricity">軌道離心率 (e)：</span>
                        <span id="val-e" class="text-blue-300 font-mono">0.017</span>
                    </label>
                    <input type="range" id="slider-e" min="0" max="0.99" step="0.001" value="0.017" class="w-full cursor-pointer">
                    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1" data-i18n="law1Desc">決定橢圓的扁平程度 (第一定律)</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Orbit Stats (Calculated) -->
            <div class="bg-slate-950 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 space-y-1 md:space-y-2 mt-auto lg:mt-0">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs md:text-sm">
                    <span class="text-slate-400" data-i18n="period">公轉週期 (T)：</span>
                    <span id="val-t" class="font-mono text-emerald-400 font-bold">2.83 yr</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs md:text-sm">
                    <span class="text-slate-400" data-i18n="t2a3">比值 (T² / a³)：</span>
                    <span class="font-mono text-emerald-400 font-bold">1.00</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Law 2: Equal Areas -->
            <div class="pt-2 border-t border-slate-700">
                <button id="btn-areas" class="w-full py-2 md:py-3 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white rounded-lg transition duration-200 font-semibold shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20 active:scale-95 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 text-sm md:text-base">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83"></path><path d="M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z"></path></svg>
                    <span data-i18n="toggleAreas">顯示掃過面積 (第二定律)</span>
                </button>
                <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2 text-center" data-i18n="law2Desc">顯示在相等時間間隔內掃過的面積。</p>
                
                <button id="btn-vectors" class="w-full py-2 md:py-3 mt-3 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white rounded-lg transition duration-200 font-semibold shadow-lg active:scale-95 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 text-sm md:text-base border border-slate-600">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                    <span data-i18n="toggleVectors">顯示速度與加速度向量</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-2 border-t border-slate-700">
                 <label class="flex justify-between text-xs md:text-sm font-medium mb-1">
                    <span data-i18n="simSpeed">模擬運行速度</span>
                    <span id="val-speed" class="text-blue-300 font-mono">0.5x</span>
                </label>
                <input type="range" id="slider-speed" min="0" max="10" step="0.1" value="0.5" class="w-full cursor-pointer">
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Canvas Container (Moved to Right) -->
        <div class="flex-grow relative bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shadow-inner min-h-[40vh] lg:min-h-0">
            <canvas id="simulationCanvas" class="block w-full h-full"></canvas>
            
            <!-- Legend overlay -->
            <div class="absolute top-2 left-2 md:top-4 md:left-4 bg-slate-950/70 p-2 md:p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 backdrop-blur-sm pointer-events-none">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_#facc15]"></div>
                    <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" data-i18n="sun">太陽 (焦點)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-blue-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_#60a5fa]"></div>
                    <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" data-i18n="planet">行星</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Vector Legends -->
                <div id="legend-vectors" class="hidden mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-slate-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                        <svg width="24" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 10" class="overflow-visible">
                            <line x1="0" y1="5" x2="20" y2="5" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="2" />
                            <polygon points="18,1 24,5 18,9" fill="#22c55e" />
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" data-i18n="legendVel">速度</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg width="24" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 10" class="overflow-visible">
                            <line x1="0" y1="5" x2="20" y2="5" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2" />
                            <polygon points="18,1 24,5 18,9" fill="#ef4444" />
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" data-i18n="legendAcc">加速度</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="flex-none bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800 p-2 md:p-3 text-center">
        <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium tracking-widest text-xs md:text-sm" data-i18n="footer">
            廠商會中學：物理科
        </p>
    </footer>

    <!-- Info Modal Overlay -->
    <div id="info-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-slate-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl max-w-3xl w-full max-h-[90vh] flex flex-col shadow-2xl overflow-hidden transform scale-95 transition-transform duration-300" id="info-modal-content">
            <div class="p-3 md:p-4 border-b border-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center bg-slate-800/50 flex-none">
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-blue-400"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 16v-4"></path><path d="M12 8h.01"></path></svg>
                    <span data-i18n="infoTitle">開普勒定律 - HKDSE 相關公式</span>
                </h2>
                <button id="btn-close-modal" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-4 md:p-6 space-y-4 md:space-y-6 overflow-y-auto flex-grow">
                <!-- Law 1 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-950/50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-2" data-i18n="law1Title">1. 第一定律：橢圓定律 (Law of Ellipses)</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3" data-i18n="info1Desc">所有行星繞太陽運行的軌道都是橢圓形，太陽位於橢圓的其中一個焦點 (Focus) 上。</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-sm md:text-base py-2 gap-2 text-slate-200">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full justify-center" data-i18n="law1Formula">
                            <div>$$a = \frac{1}{2}(\text{近日點與遠日點的距離})$$</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Law 2 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-950/50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-2" data-i18n="law2Title">2. 第二定律：等面積定律 (Law of Equal Areas)</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3" data-i18n="info2Desc">連接太陽和行星的線段在相等的時間內掃過相等的面積。因此行星在近日點速率最大，遠日點速率最小。</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Law 3 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-950/50 p-3 md:p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
                    <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-2" data-i18n="law3Title">3. 第三定律 (Third Law)</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-300 mb-3" data-i18n="info3Desc">行星公轉週期 (T) 的平方，與軌道半長軸 (a) 的立方成正比。在 DSE 必修部分中，常假設軌道為圓形 (a=r)，並以萬有引力提供向心力來推導此定律：</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-sm md:text-base py-2 gap-3 text-slate-200 bg-slate-900/50 rounded p-2">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full justify-center">
                            <span class="text-xs text-slate-400" data-i18n="lblDerive1">萬有引力 = 向心力</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full justify-center">
                            <div>$$\frac{GMm}{r^2} = m\left(\frac{2\pi}{T}\right)^2 r$$</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 w-full justify-center mt-1">
                            <div>$$T^2 = \left(\frac{4\pi^2}{GM}\right) r^3$$</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-3 md:p-4 border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-800/30 text-center flex-none">
                <button id="btn-close-modal-bottom" class="px-6 py-2 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white rounded-md transition duration-200 text-sm md:text-base" data-i18n="infoClose">關閉</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ========================================== -->
    <!-- APPLICATION LOGIC & PHYSICS ENGINE         -->
    <!-- ========================================== -->
    <script>
        // ==========================================
        // 1. DICTIONARY & LOCALIZATION (I18N)
        // ==========================================
        const i18n = {
            zh: {
                title: "開普勒行星運動定律",
                infoBtn: "說明",
                sun: "太陽",
